  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765008070\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/e0ead8cdefa0b702a5ae1c20d839de37.poster.avif?t=1765008070\" width=592 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/e0ead8cdefa0b702a5ae1c20d839de37.webm?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/e0ead8cdefa0b702a5ae1c20d839de37.mp4?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hello, dear potential player! I made a little Platformer game in which I implemented some of my ideas. Fair to say that I'm not a professional in game design and I work alone so I couldn't make everything I wanted. Nevertheless, you're gonna have:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7ac5e7195c0caf462be61bbf3e4af238.poster.avif?t=1765008070\" width=592 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7ac5e7195c0caf462be61bbf3e4af238.webm?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7ac5e7195c0caf462be61bbf3e4af238.mp4?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Comfortable controls & Impact<br></li><li> Diversity of movement mechanics<br></li><li> A lot of cool levels<br></li><li> Enjoyable minimalistic visual style<br></li><li> Total absence of the fourth wall<br></li><li> Funny story line</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7fa19078e21fc2ffa7b7a58482432a72.poster.avif?t=1765008070\" width=592 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7fa19078e21fc2ffa7b7a58482432a72.webm?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/7fa19078e21fc2ffa7b7a58482432a72.mp4?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Also about the story line! The idea is that various bloggers invaded the game and for different spoiled a nice and simple adventure by adding tons of deadly traps! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/0e8ab02a90e0ef9fd81324e1966095a1.poster.avif?t=1765008070\" width=592 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/0e8ab02a90e0ef9fd81324e1966095a1.webm?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1200450/extras/0e8ab02a90e0ef9fd81324e1966095a1.mp4?t=1765008070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>By the way, one of the main characters is me! If you try my little experiment I will be grateful! See you in the game!",
